, or to taste","1 pinch ground nutmeg              (optional)","100 g Gruyère cheese, cut in pieces","50 g shallots, halved","300 g button mushrooms, sliced","100 g ham, sliced, roughly torn in pieces"]}],"id":"r102014","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-MIQBr54xDHw\/XZQxUHRPSJI\/AAAAAAAAct0\/AXNTbyAwOVU2TMRaAlzmL4cdN_RuiYDcgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_p9IPI1EVJfuElUZy.png","title":"Ham, Mushroom and Cheese Crêpes","publishedAt":"2016-02-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"15.1 g","fat":"19.4 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"29.5 g","calories":"1475 kJ \/ 353 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, pancake pan or frying pan, small ladle, baking dish (approx. 30 cm x 22 cm), oven, hob","basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 20m","8 portions"]}